      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Richard Pijl</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:193px;\"><a href=\"http://users.telenet.be/thebaron/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/RichardPijl.jpg/191px-RichardPijl.jpg\" width=\"191\" height=\"255\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/RichardPijl.jpg/287px-RichardPijl.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/RichardPijl.jpg/382px-RichardPijl.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:RichardPijl.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Richard Pijl <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Richard Pijl</b>,<br />\na Dutch computer scientist, M.Sc. from <a href=\"/Delft_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Delft University of Technology\">Delft University of Technology</a>, and computer chess programmer. He is author of the chess engines <a href=\"/The_Baron\" title=\"The Baron\">The Baron</a> and <a href=\"/Crashtest_Dummy\" title=\"Crashtest Dummy\">Crashtest Dummy</a>. Since June 2008 Richard organized the <a href=\"/The_Chess_Programmers_Tournament\" title=\"The Chess Programmers Tournament\">The Chess Programmers Tournament</a> in Belgium, where he actually lives near the Dutch border. From December 2012 until 2016 he was the secretary of the <a href=\"/CSVN\" title=\"CSVN\">CSVN</a> board. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Pijl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/ccm6_index_news.php?id=806&amp;rubrik=6&amp;lang=0&amp;kat=6\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Pijlsvidler.JPG\" src=\"/images/e/e2/Pijlsvidler.JPG\" width=\"580\" height=\"401\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Pijl</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Svidler\">Peter Svidler</a>, Mainz 2005 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/ccm9_index_news.php?id=684&amp;rubrik=6&amp;lang=0&amp;kat=6\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Chess960-2006PijlAronian.jpg\" src=\"/images/a/a1/Chess960-2006PijlAronian.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"516\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Pijl</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chesstigers.de/index_news.php?id=622&amp;rubrik=5\">Mark Vogelgesang</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Levon_Aronian\">Levon Aronian</a>, <a href=\"/Chess960CWC_2006\" title=\"Chess960CWC 2006\">Chess960CWC 2006</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.csvn.nl/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=437%3Afotos-dag-3-29e-odccc&amp;catid=51%3Atoernooien&amp;Itemid=28&amp;lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"DeGorterPijl2009.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/95/DeGorterPijl2009.jpg/580px-DeGorterPijl2009.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"435\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/9/95/DeGorterPijl2009.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Cock_de_Gorter\" title=\"Cock de Gorter\">Cock de Gorter</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Pijl</a>, 3rd <a href=\"/DOCCC_2009\" title=\"DOCCC 2009\">DOCCC 2009</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Pijl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Richard Pijl</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>The 17th World Computer-Chess Championship</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#32_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 32, No. 2</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/WCCC_2009\" title=\"WCCC 2009\">WCCC 2009</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Pijl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://be.linkedin.com/pub/richard-pijl/6/b4a/833?trk=pub-pbmap\">Richard Pijl - Belgium | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://users.telenet.be/thebaron\">The Baron's Lair</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=88\">Richard Pijl's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/alte_daten/chesstigers_alt/Tigers/cc/2004/d/home/exhibition.htm\">The Baron vs Aronjan</a> by <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a> 2004 (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/alte_daten/chesstigers_alt/Tigers/cc/2004/d/home/artikel_04-07-31_reem_interviewt_pijl.htm\">Interview mit Richard Pijl, Programmierer des Chess960 Programms „The Baron“</a> by <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a> 2004 (German)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Richard_Pijl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://users.telenet.be/thebaron\">The Baron's Lair</a> - the home of the Baron</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/ccm6_index_news.php?id=806&amp;rubrik=6&amp;lang=0&amp;kat=6\">... weil Chess960 vom ersten Zug an spannend ist</a> (German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesstigers.de/ccm9_index_news.php?id=684&amp;rubrik=6&amp;lang=0&amp;kat=6\">2. Computer Weltmeisterschaft im Chess960</a> (German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csvn.nl/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=437%3Afotos-dag-3-29e-odccc&amp;catid=51%3Atoernooien&amp;Itemid=28&amp;lang=en\">29th Dutch Open Computer Chess Championship 2009 - Photo Gallery</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228203746\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.024 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 75/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 166/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:2413-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228203746 and revision id 11387\n -->\n"
